textAnnotations.description:
1
JUNES HAM Rows
2 c. Ground ham
3 C. Grated cheese
3 TB. onion finely chopped
TB. Worchestershire
Pepper
I Tsp. mustard
2 Raw
eggs
Mix together, split small Rolls & stuff with
ham mixture.
Bake at 375° About 10 min.
(Fills 3 Dozen small rolls.)
Vintage.Recipes/ Junes-Ham-Rolls
